        "message": {
          "id": "1509859519096815707",
          "content": "### __Have these things ready:__\n- Drop Maps (<#1188853690677870632>)\n- Loot routes (<#1131190441040162837>)\n- Surge route / Surgemap (<#1105879043175354450> / <#1174671794939121715>) \nLearn your POI. Constantly practice using your Drop Maps and Loot Routes to ensure you have the biggest advantage over the contesting team.\n\n### __Know what you do in each zone__\n- <#1336691682682474506> & <#1290897211139428362> \n- Know when you want to rotate\n- Know where you will rotate.\n\n### __Loadouts__\n- Make sure you have assigned loadouts:\n  - <#1334876131471527956>\n  - <#1334876820771835914>\n  - <#1334876910676873338>\n  - <#1334876952418324480>\n  - <#1334878595163750420>\n  - <#1334878630530121768>\n\n### __Roles__\n- Assign roles before you start playing:\n  - <#997469377261731860>\n  - <#997469379476336750>\n  - <#997469381942587432>\n  - <#1341375279331020884>\n  - <#1354582642489819287>",
